Class FrameInterval.DiscreteInterval

java.lang.Object
  au.edu.jcu.v4l4j.FrameInterval.DiscreteInterval
Enclosing class:
FrameInterval
public static class FrameInterval.DiscreteInterval
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates information about a discrete frame interval, expressed as a numerator and denominator. FrameInterval.DiscreteInterval objects are not instantiated directly, instead these objects can be obtained through a FrameInterval object.
